Package: TuneBoostTreeBayesian
Title: Bayesian Tuning for Binary Boosted Tree Models
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Joao B. G. de", "Brito", email = "JoaoSabby@users.noreply.github.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides performance-oriented Bayesian hyperparameter tuning for binary boosted tree models with XGBoost or LightGBM, cached stratified cross-validation, warm starts, early stopping, a Limbo ask/tell optimizer bridge, and optional C, Fortran, Rfast, or base R PR-AUC scoring backends.
